'''Chad N. Walker,''' ni umukinnyi wa firime muri  [[Leta Zunze Ubumwe z’Amerika|Amerika]] kandi akora na producing   . <ref>http://www.filmstarts.de/personen/689635.html</ref> <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/chad-n-walker</ref> Azwi cyane nkumuyobozi wa documentaire ''Brownstones to Red Dirt'', ''We Must Go'' . <ref name="filmy">https://africanfilmny.org/directors/chad-n-walker/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Mbere yo kuyobora documentaire, yatangiye gukora nkumuhuzabikorwa wibikorwa bigufi bya ''Magic Scarf'' . Hanyuma yinjiye nkumufasha wa Production hamwe nuwungirije umwanditsi wa firime ya firime ya ''Ice Age: The Meltdown'', ''Age Age: Umuseke wa Dinosaurs'', ''Epic'' na ''Rio'' . <ref name="filmy" /> Noneho muri 2009, yabaye umwanditsi witoza muri firime ''Horton Yumva Ninde!'' . Muri 2010, yerekanwe bwa mbere mubuyobozi hamwe na documentaire ''Brownstones kugeza Red Dirt'' . Filime izenguruka abana bamwe i Brooklyn bahinduka amakaramu yimfubyi ziva muri [[Siyera Lewone]] . Nyuma yo gutsinda kwa documentaire, yakoze documentaire ye ya kabiri ''Kei'' .

Noneho muri 2014, yakoze ''I Am Big Bird: The Caroll Spinney Story'' hamwe na Dave LaMattina . <ref>https://screenwritingmagazine.com/2015/05/18/dave-lamattina-and-chad-walker-on-i-am-big-bird-the-caroll-spinney-story/</ref><ref>https://minnesota.cbslocal.com/2015/05/12/it-aint-easy-being-big-bird/</ref>  Filime yakiriwe neza muri rusange. <ref>http://www.metacritic.com/movie/i-am-big-bird-the-caroll-spinney-story</ref> <ref>http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/i_am_big_bird_the_caroll_spinney_story/</ref> Muri 2014, yatsindiye igihembo cya Audience Choice igihembo cyiza muri Cinéfest Sudbury International Festival Festival ya film. <ref>http://www.northernlife.ca/news/lifestyle/2014/09/24-cinefest-awards-sudbury.aspx</ref>

Mu 2007, yafatanyije gushinga inzu yerekana amafilime, 'Umuringa Pot Pictures' aherekejwe na Dave LaMattina na Clay Frost. <ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/dave-lamattina/</ref>

